    "body": "Ok, so just for completeness, this would be the preferred way to align to the \"left edge\":\n\n```\n> df = pd.DataFrame([1,2,3,4,5])\n> df\n   0\n0  1\n1  2\n2  3\n3  4\n4  5\n> df2 = df.rolling(window=3).sum()\n> df2\n      0\n0   NaN\n1   NaN\n2   6.0\n3   9.0\n4  12.0\n> df2.shift(-2)\n      0\n0   6.0\n1   9.0\n2  12.0\n3   NaN\n4   NaN\n```\n"
